name: cancel unpaid order for WooCommerce
author: salah elhamouly

sections.description:
Cancel all woocommerce unpaid orders after held duration to prevent stock lock for those products you can cancel unpaid orders after some minutes or hours or days or monthes or years .

sections.installation:
1. Upload the plugin files to the /wp-content/plugins/plugin-name directory, or install the plugin through the WordPress plugins screen directly.
  2. Activate the plugin through the ‘Plugins’ screen in WordPress
sections.faq:
Where can i find the option page

in wordpress admin dashboard you will find the plugin option page called cancel order.
